help.title: Home help
help.instructions-1: Log in with a username and password
help.instructions-2: After logging in you can use keywords to search for related recipes
help.instructions-3: You can click on a recipe name to view on the recipe or you can click on two to compare their health benefits
help.instrcutions-4: Click back if you ever change your mind!
help.instructions-5: You can view the health information of a recipe from the recipe page as well!
